---
import Layout from "../layouts/MacDesktop.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
	<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 p-8">
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
			<h1 class="font-chicago text-3xl font-bold">About this site</h1>
			<a
				class="flex w-fit flex-row items-center gap-1 rounded-md border-2 border-black bg-white px-1.5 py-1 text-2xl active:border-white active:bg-black active:text-white disabled:opacity-50"
				href="/"
			>
				<i class="icon-[fa6-solid--arrow-left]"></i>
				Back to Index Page
			</a>
		</div>

		<article class="prose">
			<p>
				The design of this website is based on
				<a
					class="underline"
					href="https://www.figma.com/community/file/907684770824957775/macos-classic"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer">MacOS Classic</a
				>
				by Brett Anderson @ Figma.
			</p>

			<p>Additionally, the following open-source components are used:</p>

			<ul class="list-disc-inside">
				<li>
					<a
						class="underline"
						href="https://iconify.design"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer">iconify.design</a
					>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a
						href="https://tailwindcss.com"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="underline">TailwindCSS</a
					>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				<em>ethanlew.dev</em> is built using <i
					class="icon-[logos--astro-icon] mr-1 align-middle leading-none"></i>{
					Astro.generator
				} and is hosted by <i
					class="icon-[logos--cloudflare-workers-icon] mr-1 align-middle leading-none"
				></i>Cloudflare Pages.
			</p>
		</article>
	</div>
</Layout>
